p.paragraph.
  A form group includes multiple elements which
  aggregate to a complete form field/row.

h2.heading.heading--secondary#default Standard form group

p.paragraph.
  A normal fieldset contains a label and an input field.
  Optionally, info-icons can be added if necessary.

p.paragraph.
  Info-icons provide on click help to the user and help him better understand a particular field.

