h3.heading.heading--tertiary UX Checklist

ul.checklist
  li.checklist__item On desktop, right align labels.
  li.checklist__item On mobile, put the labels above the input element.
  li.checklist__item Mark required fiels with an asterisk*
  li.checklist__item Every label should be as clear as possible. Only add an info-icon if it really needs more explanation.
  li.checklist__item Avoid too many info-icons on one site.
  li.checklist__item Try to avoid error messages in the first place. Flexible input formats and automatic error correction may help.
  li.checklist__item Provide clear explanations instead of a generic “An error occurred”. If you don’t, your user will make the same mistake again.
